SELECT 
    'CreatePurchaseScheduleLine' || '::' || "PurchaseScheduleLine"."ID"          AS "ID",
    "PurchaseScheduleLine"."ID"                                                  AS "PurchaseScheduleLine",
    COALESCE("PurchaseScheduleLine"."CreationTime",
            "PurchaseScheduleLine_Changes"."Time")                               AS "Time",
    "PurchaseScheduleLine_Changes"."ChangedBy"                                   AS "ExecutedBy",
    "PurchaseScheduleLine_Changes"."ExecutionType"                               AS "ExecutionType",
    "PurchaseScheduleLine"."PurchaseDocumentLine_ID"                             AS "PurchaseOrderLine",
    "PurchaseScheduleLine"."PurchaseDocumentLine_ID"                             AS "PurchaseDocumentLine"
FROM "o_custom_PurchaseScheduleLine" AS "PurchaseScheduleLine"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine" AS "PurchaseDocumentLine"
        ON "PurchaseScheduleLine"."PurchaseDocumentLine_ID" = "PurchaseDocumentLine"."ID"
    LEFT JOIN "c_o_custom_PurchaseScheduleLine" AS "PurchaseScheduleLine_Changes"
        ON "PurchaseScheduleLine_Changes"."ObjectID" = "PurchaseScheduleLine"."ID"
            AND "PurchaseScheduleLine_Changes"."Attribute" = 'CreationTime'
WHERE ("PurchaseScheduleLine"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL 
    OR "PurchaseScheduleLine_Changes"."Time" IS NOT NULL)
